SOUTHERN UNION GAS CO. v. Herman T. NORMAN et al. Herman T. NORMAN et al. v. SOUTHERN UNION GAS CO. Nos. 6024, 6025. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. April 13, 1959. George T. Harris, Jr., Albuquerque,. N. M., Manuel A. Sanchez, Santa Fe,. N. M., and Willis L. Lea, Jr., Dallas, Tex.,, for appellant and cross-appellee. Frank M. Mims, Albuquerque, N. M.,. and Johnston Jeffries, Aztec, N. M., for appellees and cross-appellants.

PER CURIAM.
